<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric ideograph-other;" align="center"><b><span lang="KZ" style="font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: &#39;Arial&#39;,sans-serif;">Шанақ және ЛБЖ</span></b></p>
